Summary: Second siting of orange star like object tracking across sky, this time i got a photo
divs: Sighting DetailsHas my family left a leisure centre after swimming lessons we noticed a orange star like object slowly tacking across the sky in front of us, no noise present, people getting into an car commented on the object, what could it be? thats strange. We all took photos. It appeared the same as the object I witnessed last night and reported on the MUFON website. The object traveled into the distance the traveled out of sight in an instant.
